  "local_port": 50340,
  "remote_port": 443,
  "prompt": "Which are the best resources to learn AngularJs2 and Typescript?",
  "response": "Learning Angular and TypeScript can be quite rewarding if you use the right resources. Here are some of the best resources to get started:\n\n### Angular\n1. **Official Angular Documentation**: The official Angular documentation is comprehensive and includes tutorials, guides, and API references. It's a great place to start:\n   - [Angular Documentation](https://angular.io/docs)\n\n2. **Angular University**: This website offers high-quality courses on various aspects of Angular, from beginner-level tutorials to advanced topics.\n   - [Angular University](https://angular-university.io/)\n\n3. **Udemy**: Udemy has several popular Angular courses. Some top-rated courses include \"Angular - The Complete Guide\" by Maximilian Schwarzm\u00fcller.\n   - [Udemy Angular Courses](https://www.udemy.com/)\n\n4. **Coursera**: You can find courses from reputable institutions that cover Angular in different contexts, often including project-based learning.\n   - [Coursera Angular Courses](https://www.coursera.org/)\n\n5. **Egghead.io**: This platform offers concise, high-quality videos on various programming topics, including Angular.\n   - [Egghead Angular Courses](https://egghead.io/q/angular)\n\n### TypeScript\n1. **Official TypeScript Documentation**: The official docs are a great place to start, with tutorials, examples, and comprehensive explanations of TypeScript features.\n   - [TypeScript Documentation](https://www.typescriptlang.org/docs/)\n\n2. **TypeScript Deep Dive**: This is a free online book by Basarat Ali Syed that covers TypeScript in-depth.\n   - [TypeScript Deep Dive](https://basarat.gitbook.io/typescript/)\n\n3. **Udemy**: Similar to Angular, Udemy offers a variety of TypeScript courses. One popular course is \"Understanding TypeScript\" by Maximilian Schwarzm\u00fcller.\n   - [Udemy TypeScript Courses](https://www.udemy.com/)\n\n4. **Pluralsight**: Provides quality video tutorials on TypeScript, often focusing on practical applications.\n   - [Pluralsight TypeScript Courses](https://www.pluralsight.com/)\n\n5. **Egghead.io**: High-quality video tutorials on TypeScript that cover a wide range of topics.\n   - [Egghead TypeScript Courses](https://egghead.io/q/typescript)\n\n### Additional Resources\n- **YouTube**: There are countless free tutorials and conferences that cover both Angular and TypeScript.\n   - [Academind YouTube Channel](https://www.youtube.com/channel/UCSJbGtTlrDami-tDGPUV9-w)\n   - [Traversy Media YouTube Channel](https://www.youtube.com/user/TechGuyWeb)\n\n- **Stack Overflow & Community Forums**: Engaging with the community can help answer specific questions you might have as you learn.\n   - [Stack Overflow Angular](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/angular)\n   - [Stack Overflow TypeScript](https://stackoverflow.com/questions/tagged/typescript)\n\nBy combining these resources, you should have a comprehensive foundation to learn and master Angular and TypeScript. Happy coding!",
